{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b93f197a60","title":"交大西安部分出現反动标語","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5d8863424e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":12,"articleId":"b93f197a60"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c9caa7d8bc","type":"title","text":"交大西安部分出现反动标语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b93f197a60"},{"id":"8080ae2cd4","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社西安12日电   交通大学西安部分出现辱駡共产党的反动标语和言论。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b93f197a60"},{"id":"d730f6c25c","type":"paragraph","text":"11日发现的一张贴在一个自修敎室的反动标语写道：“打倒毛贼东，建立‘自由中国’”在校内厕所、走廊、敎室内又分别发现了“‘猪’，‘毛’喽喽！共产党员若不允返沪，请当心！”、“推翻共产党、打回老家去！”、“打倒共产党，毛主席逝世”、“共产党员混蛋”等好几张反动标语。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b93f197a60"},{"id":"938202d69f","type":"paragraph","text":"目前，交大西安部分校方已将部分反动标语公布，许多敎员和学生为此出了大字报，对上述情况表示愤慨，要求大家正常进行迁校问题的讨论，但必须提高警惕。（孙传镐）","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b93f197a60"},{"id":"736396f8ee","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：新华通讯社编：《内部参考》，第2230期，1957年6月14日。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b93f197a60"}],"page":{"id":"293b78ab8d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b93f197a60","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}